<div class="container-fluid">
  <h1 class="mt-4"><a href="/users">Users</a></h1>
  <h2>Get requests</h2>
  <p>Example get request that returns all users in a JSON format:</p>
  <pre>
    <code>
     curl 'http://35.234.67.178/users'
    </code>
  </pre>
  <p>A query can be performed to return a specific user</p>
  <h5>Example query:</h5>
  <pre>
     <code>
          curl 'http://35.234.67.178/users?user_id=2'
     </code>
  </pre>
  <h2>Post requests</h2>
  <p>Example post request that inserts a new user into the database:</p>
  <pre>
    <code>
      curl --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
      --request POST \
      --data '{"first_name": "Joe", "middle_name": "Jack", "last_name": "Doe",
               "phone_number": 789456123, "email": "Joe@doe.test"}' \
      http://35.234.67.178/users
    </code>
  </pre>
  <h2>Delete requests</h2>
  <p>Example delete request that deletes one user from the database:</p>
  <pre>
    <code>
      curl \
      --request DELETE \
      http://35.234.67.178/users\?user_id=7
    </code>
  </pre>
  <p>Example delete request that deletes all of the users from the database:</p>
  <pre>
    <code>
      curl \
      --request DELETE \
      http://35.234.67.178/users
    </code>
  </pre>
  <h2>Put requests</h2>
  <p>Example put request that updates all fields of a user in the database:</p>
  <pre>
    <code>
      curl --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
      --request PUT \
      --data '{"first_name": "Jack", "middle_name": "Joe", "last_name": "Doe",
               "phone_number": 789456123, "email": "Jack@doe.test"}' \
      http://35.234.67.178/users\?user_id=2
    </code>
  </pre>
  <h2>Patch requests</h2>
  <p>Example patch request that updates some fields of a user in the database:</p>
  <pre>
    <code>
      curl --header "Content-Type: application/json" \
      --request PATCH \
      --data '{"first_name":"John"}' \
      http://35.234.67.178/users\?user_id=4
    </code>
  </pre>
</div>
